Union MaybeI32 has none; some value: i32.

To unwrap positive maybe: MaybeI32, giving i32.
Require match maybe:
MaybeI32.some with value gives value is greater than 0;
otherwise gives false.
Give match maybe:
MaybeI32.some with value gives value;
otherwise gives 0.

To main, giving i32.
Give unwrap positive MaybeI32.some with value be 7.
